OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRogers outage: Millions to 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fget credits over internet  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fand mobile blackout        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Canadian mobile and internet giant     
OL,6, Rogers says it will give credits to    
OL,7, millions of its customers after a      
OL,8, nationwide outage last week.           
OL,10,FIn a statement posted late on Tuesday, 
OL,11,Fthe firm said users will receive "the  
OL,12,Fequivalent of five days service".      
OL,14,FThe outage - which lasted for more than
OL,15,F15 hours - also affected transport,    
OL,16,Fbanking and emergency services.        
OL,18,FRegulators have ordered the company to 
OL,19,Fprovide an account of "why" and "how"  
OL,20,Fthe disruption happened.               
